<h1><b>Personal Agency</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;&ndash; the ability for a person to act or intervene to produce a particular effect or result.</span></h1>
<h1><b>&nbsp;</b></h1>
<h1><b>Opportunity</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;- A time or set of circumstances that makes it possible to do something.</span></h1>
